eight: 400\">Apart from other applications, <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\/what-is-ethereum-a-step-by-step-guide\/\">Ethereum (ETH)<\/a> is rapidly emerging as one of the most popular cryptocurrencies for real estate purchases. Pacaso, a real estate company, now accepts cryptocurrency for second home acquisitions, making it the first marketplace of this kind to do so.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The adoption of cryptocurrency as a form of payment is increasing, as there are already various companies that allow users to actually use their cryptocurrencies. Companies accepting bitcoins via BitPay include Newegg, SlingTV, Twitch, Jomashop, APMEX, the American Cancer Society, Namecheap, and the Dallas Mavericks.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Particularly, the Mavericks became the first sports team in the major leagues to adopt cryptocurrencies. The Sacramento Kings of the NBA and the Carolina Hurricanes of the NHL are two additional sports teams that take cryptocurrency via BitPay. Porsche Towson, the only private Porsche facility in Baltimore, has collaborated with BitPay to support a variety of digital assets, including <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\/shiba-outperforms-doge-in-february\/\">Shiba Inu (SHIB)<\/a>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\/jeff-wyler-automotive-family-accepts-payment-in-ethereum\/\">Jeff Wyler Automotive Family is the First Car Dealership to Accept Payment in Ethereum<\/a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\">Crypto Academy<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><br \/>\n<br \/><a href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\/jeff-wyler-automotive-family-accepts-payment-in-ethereum\/\">Source link <\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ethereum (ETH), the second-biggest cryp